<hr>How could we add Portraits?
<p>
In the Wiki?  To add an image to a page just type in its URL and the Wiki will figure it out.  For example just put <b>http://www.twinked.com/forums/DoT_Sword.jpg</b> in the text and you get this: 
<p>
<img src="http://www.twinked.com/forums/DoT_Sword.jpg">
<p>
There is a good tutorial at <a href="wiki.pl?Intro_and_Tour">Intro and Tour</a>.  The specifics on adding links is at <a href="wiki.pl?References_and_Links">References and Links</a>.
